description.en:
HODLers of 50K will be able to earn 50C during expansion via staking their 50K tokens in
the boardroom. These 50C are generated by the smart contract upon each epoch if 50C TWAP is above $0.5. The amount will be 2.5% of the current 50C total supply, half of which will be send to the boardroom for HODLers to claim.
